Package: nmathresh
Type: Package
Title: Thresholds and invariant intervals for Network Meta-Analysis
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("David", "Phillippo", email="david.phillippo@bristol.ac.uk", role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to calculate decision-invariant
    bias-adjustment thresholds and intervals for a Bayesian Network Meta-Analysis,
    as described in Phillippo et al. (2016).
License: GPL-3
